    <div class="faq-card">
      <div class="faq-q" onclick="this.parentNode.classList.toggle('open')">
        Provisioning a new ONU/ONT for a subscriber
      </div>
      <div class="faq-a">
        <ol>
          <li>Add the customer in Admin Portal &rarr; Subscribers &rarr; Add. Note Subscriber ID &amp; plan.</li>
          <li>Open the GenieACS UI and find the ONU by serial number or MAC.</li>
          <li>Open the device detail page &rarr; Parameters &rarr; expand <code>InternetGatewayDevice.WANDevice.1.WANConnectionDevice.1.WANPPPConnection.1</code>.</li>
          <li>Set <code>Username</code> = subscriber's RADIUS username; <code>Password</code> = RADIUS password; <code>Enable</code> = true.</li>
          <li>Apply changes. GenieACS pushes on the next Inform (~30s).</li>
          <li>Verify in Admin Portal &rarr; Online Users.</li>
        </ol>
        <p><strong>Tip:</strong> Save common ONU configurations as Presets (Admin &rarr; Presets) so future ONUs of the same vendor auto-apply.</p>
