        Day-to-day GenieACS operator tasks
      </div>
      <div class="faq-a">
        <h4>Reboot a customer's ONU remotely</h4>
        <ol><li>Find the device.</li><li>Actions &rarr; Reboot. Device drops for 30-60s and re-informs.</li></ol>
