        <ol>
          <li>Open device detail page.</li>
          <li>Edit <code>InternetGatewayDevice.LANDevice.1.WLANConfiguration.1.SSID</code> and <code>.PreSharedKey.1.KeyPassphrase</code>.</li>
          <li>Apply (some firmwares require a reboot).</li>
        </ol>
        <h4>Bulk firmware upgrade</h4>
        <ol>
          <li>Upload firmware via Admin &rarr; Files.</li>
          <li>Create a Preset targeting the vendor/model + <code>DownloadDiagnosticState</code>.</li>
          <li>Apply preset to the target device group.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-card">
      <div class="faq-q" onclick="this.parentNode.classList.toggle('open')">
        Troubleshooting common GenieACS errors
      </div>
      <div class="faq-a">
        <h4>ONU doesn't appear in GenieACS</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>ACS URL on the ONU must match the CWMP listener exactly (trailing slash matters).</li>
          <li>TCP 7547 inbound must be open from the subscriber network.</li>
          <li>Reboot the ONU and watch <code>journalctl -fu genieacs-cwmp</code>.</li>
        </ul>
        <h4>Inform received but parameters not pushed</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Open device &rarr; Tasks queue, look for failed tasks.</li>
          <li>Verify <code>ManagementServer.Username</code> / <code>.Password</code> on the ONU match the GenieACS security realm.</li>
        </ul>
        <h4>Services not starting after reboot</h4>
        <pre>sudo systemctl restart genieacs-cwmp genieacs-fs genieacs-ui genieacs-nbi
journalctl -u genieacs-cwmp -n 100 --no-pager</pre>
      </div>
    </div>

